column4: Features:This little device fits on most taps and lights up a set of LEDs when you turn onthe tap. Transforming the stream of water into a beautiful waterfall of light.The sensitive faucet light will change colors according to the temperature of water.The color's change remind you the water's temperature.Water flash red when temperature above 50°CWater glows Red when water is Hot (temperature above 42°C).Water glows Green when water is Warm (temperature is 33°C - 41°C).Water glows Blue when water is Cold (temperature below 32°C).No batteries and external power supply, it will illuminate after water flows down.Offer you a delight & wonderful experience.ABS chroming material, excellent corrosion resistance, durable.Ideal for bathroom or kitchen to make it fantastic.Direction for use:Firstly, take off net from tap screw thread.Secondly, install LED faucet light screw thread.Thirdly, usage of adapter screw thread inside universal adapter.（adapter screw thread not included）Note:Automatic generation without batteriesSpecifications:Original box: NOCase material: ABSLED emitting color: Green, Red & BlueInternal diameter: 15mmExternal thread diameter: 23.5mmItem size: 35 * 24 * 24mmItem weight: 20gPackage weight: 29gColor: SilverPacking content:1 x LED light faucet
